Unified Jenkins Pipeline Flow:

1) Checkout code for frontend, backend, and DB.

2) Build & test each tier.

3) Dockerize & push images to ECR.

4) Update manifests (frontend-deployment.yaml, backend-deployment.yaml, db-statefulset.yaml).

5) Commit & push manifest changes to Git.

6) ArgoCD syncs and applies changes to staging/production cluster.

7) Do it anyway
